# STIG: WN10-CC-000005 â€“ Disable Lock Screen Camera

## ðŸ” Overview

This STIG requires disabling **camera access on the Windows 10 lock screen** to prevent unauthorized interaction with the device before user authentication.

- **STIG ID:** WN10-CC-000005  
- **Rule Title:** Camera access from the lock screen must be disabled  
- **Required Value:** Enabled (`NoLockScreenCamera = 1`)

## âš™ï¸ What This Script Does

- Creates the required registry path
- Sets the value to disable camera use while on the lock screen

